<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM9.4.5">
<l>villā lilaṅkai malaṅkac caranturanta</l>
<l>vallāḷaṉ piṉpōṉa neñcam varumaḷavum</l>
<l>ellāru meṉṟaṉṉai yēcilum pēciṭiṉum</l>
<l>pullāṇi yemperumāṉ poykēṭ ṭiruntēṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Even if everyone scolds me, even if they talk,</l>
<l>Until my heart, which followed the mighty lord</l>
<l>Who discharged arrows with his bow to trouble Laṅkā,</l>
<l>Returns, I stay in Pullāṇi, listening to the lies of our lord.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
